Package: nlirp
Title: Natural Language Item Response Processing - Multilingual Semantic Scoring for Open Responses
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Joost", "Kruis", email = "joost.kruis@cito.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Estimate expected scores for open-ended item responses by
 leveraging spaCy language models. The package preprocesses response
 text, optionally performs spellchecking, derives document embeddings,
 and propagates human scores from semantically similar answers. Any
 installed spaCy model can be used so Dutch, English, or other
 languages can share a single scoring pipeline.
